"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1931452-Andy-Murray-Olympics-2024-retirement-Taylor-Fritz-Tommy-Paul\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Andy Murrayreceived an apology immediately after entering retirement at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 87, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In his final tournament, the former world No.\", \"from\": 88, \"to\": 133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 paired up withDan Evansin the men's doubles event and made it all the way to the quarter-final.\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But theysuffered a one-sided 6-1 6-4 defeatto American duo Taylor Fritz and Tommy Paul on Thursday night, just missing out on the medal rounds.\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 279, \"end\": 287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9958916215373125, \"rank\": 0.004122309503632178, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 292, \"end\": 304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taylor Fritz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\"}, {\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.688208236728543e-18, \"text\": \"Tommy Paul\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the match, Fritz confessed that he said sorry to Murray at the net and did not take pride in being the one to end the three-time Grand Slam champion's career.\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0260996415456897e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously we want to win like we were pumped up to win.\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it is sad I guess to see it end for Andy, he's someone that I think both of us have looked up to for a very long time,\\\" the world No.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"12 said.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's a great guy so I guess I do not take like, a lot of pride in doing it.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 825, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But you know, we are here.\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are here to try and win a medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was an emotional night on Court Suzanne Lenglen, withboth Murray and Evans in tears.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 919, \"end\": 940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Court Suzanne Lenglen\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it was a strange feeling for the Americans, who struggled to celebrate as usual.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sharing what he told Murray at the net, Fritz added: \\\"I just said like, I do not even know what, I feel like I said like, sorry.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1085, \"end\": 1091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0260996415456897e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And like and also like congrats on the career but I do not really know what to say to him.\\\"\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just in:Carlos Alcaraz thrashes Auger-Aliassime as Spaniard one win from Olympic gold  Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1294, \"end\": 1308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    They were in a similar position at the 2022 Laver Cup -Roger Federer's retirement tournament.\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1588, \"end\": 1601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roger Federer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Swiss star teamed up withRafael Nadalin doubles but they lost to Team World's Jack Sock and Frances Tiafoe.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1631, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swiss_people\", \"score\": 0.6776844652039669, \"rank\": 0.4116421719642674, \"text\": \"Swiss\", \"t