ies\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And also both of us know it's just a better combo with me serving and Tommy at the net than him serving and me at the net.\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3220, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we felt pretty comfortable serving that one out at the last game.\\\"\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fritz has come a long way since his first encounter with Murray, when he was a teenager invited to practice with the two-time gold medallist at the ATP Finals when they were held in London.\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3349, \"end\": 3355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0260996415456897e-48, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 3474, \"end\": 3480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.942032245229692, \"rank\": 0.06153070952337954, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recalling their initial meeting, he said: \\\"I think it might have been when I was going to the World Tour Finals like as a 17-year-old.\", \"from\": 3482, \"to\": 3616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3576, \"end\": 3593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATP_Finals\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.214091374432802e-18, \"text\": \"World Tour Finals\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATP_Finals\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATP_Finals\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I was accepting something I think for being the youngest in the top 100 and I was warming him up.\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was crazy because I was jet lagged and he wanted to practice at like 8am every morning.\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I was practising with him at 8am every morning for World Tour Finals because he was getting ready to play Cilic so I was like his practice partner for that.\\\"\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3870, \"end\": 3887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATP_Finals\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.214091374432802e-18, \"text\": \"World Tour Finals\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATP_Finals\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATP_Finals\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3978, \"to\": 4147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4115, \"end\": 4128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.547177029866398e-23, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 4149, \"to\": 4216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4164, \"end\": 4177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.547177029866398e-23, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"